{"lemma":"عَقاراتٌ","slug":"عَقاراتٌ","root":"ع.ق.ر","root_slug":"ع-ق-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ق-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n29916","n29917","n29922"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"real estate, immovable property"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"drug, pharmacum, chemical substance that becomes active in the human body"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"wine that does not delay to intoxicate, hooch","tags":["poetic","uncountable"],"examples":[{"text":"كـَأَنَّ فَاهَا (var. فِيهَا) عـُقَارًا قَرْقَفًا (var. عـُقَارٌ قَرْقَفٌ) نُشَّ (var. سُنَّ) مِنَ الدَنِّ فَالْكَأْسُ رَذُوم","english":"As if her mouth were a gassing hooch … poured from the jug so the stoop was about to overflow"},{"text":"طَرِبَ ٱلشَّيْخُ فَغَنَّى، وَٱصْطَبَحْ\nمِنْ عُقَارٍ تُنْهِبُ ٱلْهَمَّ ٱلْفَرَحْ\nأَخَذْتْ مِنْ كُلِّ شَيْءٍ لَوْنَهَا،\nهِيَ فِي نَاجُودِهَا قَوْسُ قُزَحْ\nشَيْخُ لِذَّاتٍ، نَقِيٌّ عِرْضُهُ،\nتَحْسُنُ ٱلْأَشْعَارُ فِيهِ، وَٱلْمِدَحْ.\nلَا تَرَاهُ ٱلدَّهْرُ إِلَّا ثَمِلاً،\nبَيْنَ إِبْرِيقٍ، وَزِقٍّ، وَقَدَحْ","english":"The shaykh gleed and sang and craved more booze\nforthy delight removes the sorrow.\nHe obtained from every thing its hues\nand his cup exposed a rainbow.\nShaykh of bliss, no way blammed,\nThe notes of him are merry, fele to plaud,\nFate sees him not but slammed,\nbetwixe ewer and wineskin, beaker-pawed."}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Borrowed from Aramaic עִיקָּרָא / ܥܶܩܳܪܳܐ (ʿiqqārā, ʿeqqārā, “root; drug”), doublet of عِرْق (ʕirq, “root”).\n\nAnother borrowing of Aramaic עִיקָּרָא / ܥܶܩܳܪܳܐ (ʿiqqārā, ʿeqqārā), triplet of the former."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n29916","headword_ar":"عَقَارٌ","root":"Eqr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaqara Aln~axolapa","text_ar":"عَقَرَ النَّخْلَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Real,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"immovable, property,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kul~u maAlK lahu A^aSolN","text_ar":"كُلُّ مَالٍ لَهُ اَصْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", Mgh, or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"milokN","text_ar":"مِلْكٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaAbitN lahu A^aSolN","text_ar":"ثَابِتٌ لَهُ اَصْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", Msb, or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA lahu A^aSolN waqaraArN","text_ar":"مَا لَهُ اَصْلٌ وَقَرَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", KT,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an estate"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consisting of a house"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land yielding a revenue;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as land and a house;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(KT;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as a house and palm-trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or simply,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land yielding a revenue;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DayoEapN","text_ar":"ضَيْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Mgh, K:) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuqoraY","text_ar":"عُقْرَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Sgh, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lands yielding revenues"},{"kind":"text","text":"(syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DiyaAEN","text_ar":"ضِيَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"); and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"palmtrees;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"palm-trees"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in particular:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaqaAy^iru","text_ar":"عَقَايِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"page_break","n":2110},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA lahu daArN walaA EaqaArN","text_ar":"مَا لَهُ دَارٌ وَلَا عَقَارٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has not a house nor land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lands yielding revenues,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"palm-trees."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.) ―         -b2-  Also (sometimes, Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Household goods,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"furniture and utensils,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, * K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which are not used except on the occasions of festivals,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and necessary affairs of great importance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) thus, with fet-h, accord. to AZ and IAar; (TA;) and sometimes with damm [↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuqaArN","text_ar":"عُقَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (K,) thus accord. to As; (O, TA;) but in saying so, he differs from the generality of authorities: (TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"best"},{"kind":"text","text":"of furniture and the like, because none but the best is spread on the occasions of festivals: (TA:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"best"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything. (O, TA.) One says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Albayoti EaqaArN","text_ar":"فِى البَيْتِ عَقَارٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HasanN","text_ar":"حَسَنٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In the house,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tent, are goodly furniture and utensils."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","Mgh","K","Sgh","TA","L"]},{"entry_id":"n29917","headword_ar":"عُقَارٌ","root":"Eqr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wine:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wine that does not delay to intoxicate:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) so called because of its taking hold upon the intellect, or contending with it for superiority, ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liA^an~ahaA EaAqarati AlEaqola","text_ar":"لِاَنَّهَا عَاقَرَتِ العَقْلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) accord. to Aboo-Nasr; (S;) or because of its remaining long confined to the [jar called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dan~","text_ar":"دَنّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) accord. to AA; (S, O;) [see 3;] or because the drinker keeps closely to it; (TA;) or because it prevents the drinker from walking; (K;) or because it disables ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaEoqiru","text_ar":"يَعْقِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":") the intellect. (IAar.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaqaArN","text_ar":"عَقَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n29922","headword_ar":"عَقَّارٌ","root":"Eqr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A simple; a drug;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any of the elements"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uSuwl","text_ar":"اُصُول"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of medicines;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is used medicinally, of plants"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of their roots"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uSuwl","text_ar":"اُصُول"},{"kind":"text","text":") and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) [accord. to the CK,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is used medicinally, of plants,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of their roots:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the last word being in the nom. case:] as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eiq~iyrN","text_ar":"عِقِّيرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is used medicinally, of plants"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a medicine that is used for moving the bowels:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any curative plant;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also its pl., (AHeyth,) which is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaqaAqiyru","text_ar":"عَقَاقِيرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (AHeyth, S:) nothing thus termed is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuwhN","text_ar":"فُوهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (AHeyth.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadiydN jay~idu","text_ar":"حَدِيدٌ جَيِّدُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEaqaAqiyri","text_ar":"العَقَاقِيرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Iron of excellent manufacture."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","L","Az","AHeyth","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}